TBI + OUD + PTSD + depression + homeless: integrated multidisciplinary + Housing First. TBI cog + pain multimodal + MAT buprenorphine + trauma-focused CBT + SSRI/SNRI + sleep + suicide risk + housing + benefits + trauma-informed + cultural humility. Modern: integrated equity.'
